---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="20 Years of Medical Scrubs Manufacturing Excellence | Yilong History" 
  description="Born in the heart of Anhui, China, Yilong Scrubs has spent 20 years perfecting medical uniforms. We are a dedicated factory 100% focused on scrubs."
  keywords="scrub manufacturer history, medical apparel factory China, nursing uniform craftsmanship, professional scrub manufacturing"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary font-bold rounded-full text-sm mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Our Story</div>
      <h1 class="text-6xl font-black mb-12 italic">20 Years of Craftsmanship</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-xl prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-16">
        <p>In 2006, in the heart of Anhui, China, a vision was born: to create medical apparel that doesn't just look professional, but feels like a second skin. Anhui Yilong Environmental Protection Technology Co., Ltd. began its journey with a singular focus—medical scrubs. For two decades, we have remained 100% dedicated to this craft.</p>
        
        <p>Our story is one of evolution. We've seen medical uniforms transition from simple cotton garments to high-tech, performance-driven gear. By staying ahead of textile innovation, we've developed our signature 4-way stretch fabrics that are now OEKO-TEX® Standard 100 certified, ensuring safety for those who spend their lives saving others.</p>
        
        <p>Today, Yilong Scrubs serves healthcare brands across North America, Europe, and Australia. We are more than a factory; we are a strategic partner for brands that demand quality without compromise.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden mb-24 h-[400px]">
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A3fde98c1bef74e8281a6bb7fd8fd2012X.png" alt="Yilong Scrubs Manufacturing Facility" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 py-16 border-y border-slate-100 mb-16">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-primary mb-2">20</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Years Experience</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-secondary mb-2">100%</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Scrubs Focused</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl font-black text-orange-600 mb-2">Global</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Market Reach</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-12 rounded-3xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-6 italic">Global Reach</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Serving healthcare brands in North America, Europe, and Australia with high-performance medical apparel.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-12 rounded-3xl">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl mb-6 italic">Factory Direct</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">No middlemen. You get direct access to our 20 years of manufacturing know-how and competitive pricing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>